{"tid":2373163,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"Netflix全球訂戶突破2億！《Sweet Home》、《今際之國》觀看量揭曉","createTime":"2021-01-20T08:54:26.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-21T08:03:47.000Z","uid":109923,"like":70,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":52,"replies":[{"pid":"bbc7accdb011f6feb2f62ccc406181460f375698","tid":2373163,"uid":109923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T08:54:26.000Z","msg":"隨著串流大戰開打，向來居龍頭位置的 Netflix 也不免受到強敵 Disney+ 和 HBO Max 來襲的影響。然而，由於去年爆發的新冠肺炎疫情，使得人們待在家中的時間拉長，不少人也因此加入追劇一族的行列，這讓 Netflix 因而受惠，在去年一整年新增了近 3700 萬訂戶，使總數突破 2 億大關。<br />\n<br />\n....<br />\n<br />\n而在亞洲原創部分，韓劇《Sweet Home》有 2200 萬觀看數、日劇《今際之國的闖關者》（Alice in Borderland）則有 1800 萬。"},{"pid":"203eca50c93e13e4aa125fb79cfcd6d2de64c8b9","tid":2373163,"uid":40267,"like":36,"dislike":3,"score":33,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T09:01:48.000Z","msg":"支那人話禾地有愛奇藝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9093a099b8e07553dabb43ef13a779fdd0b749a5","tid":2373163,"uid":41818,"like":5,"dislike":8,"score":-3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T09:18:34.000Z","msg":"Disney+個勢都勁"},{"pid":"fdcd1a90fe1302f66b982d166c5d590c1a958760","tid":2373163,"uid":217565,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"9093a099b8e07553dabb43ef13a779fdd0b749a5","tid":2373163,"uid":41818,"like":5,"dislike":8,"score":-3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T09:18:34.000Z","msg":"Disney+個勢都勁"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T09:22:53.000Z","msg":"有咩劇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8eadacf0c74d20780d01ab791c70e8e1a84163ed","tid":2373163,"uid":44674,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"fdcd1a90fe1302f66b982d166c5d590c1a958760","tid":2373163,"uid":217565,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"9093a099b8e07553dabb43ef13a779fdd0b749a5","tid":2373163,"uid":41818,"like":5,"dislike":8,"score":-3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T09:18:34.000Z","msg":"Disney+個勢都勁"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T09:22:53.000Z","msg":"有咩劇<img src=\"/asse